  "title": "Type-Checking Cron-Driven Tasks Using FastAPI in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide demonstrates how to leverage FastAPI for type checking cron-driven tasks in Python 3.12+. It involves creating an API endpoint for your task and using dependency injection for the execution of the task.",
